-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gridx - Incubation for the next generation of Grid
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author: Xiao Wen Zhu(Oliver), Pei Wang(Nate), Wei Huang(Evan), Qiang Wang(Elvis)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:

	Gridx is an incubation project as a basis for the next generation of Dojo Grid.
	The key idea is to set up a highly extensible core and a rich set of modules to be loaded on demand,
	based on that appropriate modules can be picked up to consist different Grid instances
	in order to meet a wide range of requirements - MiniGrid(MobileGrid), AdvancedGrid, TreeGrid etc.
	Check out this demo and see how Gridx is running much more faster and flexible!
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

	Dojo Core
	Dijit
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions

	Simply run the included demo.html
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
